text: Kiska-Yelga () is a rural locality (a village) in Tatar-Ulkanovsky Selsoviet, Tuymazinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 71 as of 2010. There are 6 streets. == Geography == It is located 8 km from Tuymazy, 4 km from Tatar-Ulkanovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Tuymazinsky District
title: Kiska-Yelga, Tuymazinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
